Package: Arachnomicon
Type: Package
Title: Taxonomic Standardization of Spider Species Names Using WSC and GBIF
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Victor",
      family = "Lobato dos Santos",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "vlobatosantos@gmail.com"
    )
Description: 
    Tools to standardize and resolve spider species names using the World Spider
    Catalogue (via 'arakno') and GBIF (via 'rgbif'). The package corrects outdated
    nomenclature, resolves synonyms, retrieves LSIDs, and optionally returns
    taxonomic family information. Includes caching and checkpoint mechanisms
    for efficient large-scale queries.
Maintainer: Victor Lobato dos Santos <vlobatosantos@gmail.com>
